==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Misle
<hw>Mi"sle</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A fine rain; a thick mist; a mizzle;
a drizzle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

